value.string: This home has lots of possibilities - one legal ohana and downstairs of home can be turned into seperate dwelling. Ocean views - Vaulted ceilings lots of skylights - large corner lot - cannot be seen from street - shared driveway Short sale - Please submit all short sale addendums and "as is" addendum-
Front house 4 bdrm 2 bath was remodeled , new electrical, plumbing, appliances, light fixtures, new cabinets,,floors and granite counter tops all done 2007.The back 2 story has 3 bdrm 3 bath.

A great opportunity to have a large and well built home that has more than enough room for a growing family. The main home features a large open kitchen and dining area with stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, and warm wood cabinets. The living room expands into the outside lanai filled with bamboo , red palms for more outdoor living potential. One bedroom / bath is located downstairs . Upstairs is a large master bedroom and bath with a large lanai and ocean views. Large bedrooms and an office complete the upstairs living. The Ohana is an additional home of 3 bedrooms / 1bath that has its own separate entrance. Close to all the schools and conveniently located above Lahaina town. Please do not disturb the occupants.

Panoramic ocean views throughout this gorgeous remodel in Waiehu Terrace. Large open floor plan with New Tile Floors, Kitchen, Bathrooms, high-end Maytag appliances, windows, roof. Move in ready!!! Plenty of off-Street parking. Property can either be a 5BR 3 Bath 1600 sq ft single family home or 3/2 plus 1/1 Ohana. Ohana has optional finishes for buyer.
Fantastic 3 island ocean views. Loads of potential. Great property for creative people. Property is being sold "as is".

Panoramic ocean and South Maui views abound from the deck above this impressive family home. The spacious single level 3 bedroom main living area features an open floor plan with a large gourmet kitchen, beautiful wood floors and custom marble and tile work throughout. A two story newer addition is charming and features a "mariner's viewing deck" on the roof. The converted garage features plenty of extra family space. A large laundry room and storage room is accessible off the garage. Private yards are fully landscaped with timed irrigation system, mature fruit trees and privacy hedge. This well maintained property features a new roof, two new solar hot water heaters, new upper deck stairs and roofing, and many new upgraded ceiling fans, carpeting, appliances and interior paint throughout. County tax records may vary from the description of the property. Buyers to do their own due diligence.

Absolutely the Best Value and Most Finished Square Feet you will find for your money in Kula! On this very private 2.5acres, you will find a well thought out 2,798SF Upcountry Family Home with loads of multiple bonus structures (all county approved & permitted) A giant 5,000 SF separate “Workspace” (with 3 Phase 440 Power), a 1700SF Studio and a 616 SF semi-attached Guest Ohana; perfect for “You Name It”…rentable space, your own home based business, additional living space for friends, family guests, kids game/theatre rooms, a yoga/wellness retreat, brewery, surf board shaping shop, bed and breakfast – whatever you dream or envision. Enjoy absolute perfect weather (according the National Geographic the most pleasant weather on Earth!) Very close to THE most sought after schools on Maui - Waldorf, Seabury Hall, Kamehameha, Kula Elementary. This is truly the best of ALL worlds. This home has a make sense layout with lots of room, incredible Koa wood finishes throughout, paved driveway, professional landscaping, awesome bi-coastal views. This is a one-owner home, and was built by the seller who is a professional builder. It therefore has all of the upgrades, meticulous maintenance and quality of construction you would expect. Price has been drastically reduced for quick sale.

There are 4 separate units in this home. Easy access to Napili beaches and West side surf spots. Currently tenant occupied. The larger upstairs units are light, bright and airy with ocean views. Spiral staircases lead to loft area. The 2 ground level units are 1 bed/ 1 bath "ohana" type units with loft storage. Each unit has a one car garage. All living spaces have their own washer / dryer. This is a non-conforming property and buyer to do their own due diligence. Prequalified buyers with 48 hours notice to show.
